---
title: Fajita-Spiced Chicken & Black Bean Bowls with Dark Meat Chicken, Cotija Cheese & Lime Crema
description: Mexican-style rice bowls are always welcome on our table, and this one is an instant winner. You'll sizzle up juicy spiced dark meat chicken and serve it over a bed of fluffy rice. Top with zesty lime crema, and serve alongside mashed black beans sprinkled with crumbled cotija cheese. A squeeze of lime juice just before serving brings it all together.
